{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"level":1,"content":"如何在Roam-CSS-System的基础上优化调整出自己需要的roam样式"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"TOC / 内容提要","level":3},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":3,"content":"Bear + Roam, 有没有搞头?"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>一直很喜欢Roam的流畅，也很喜欢Bear笔记的高颜值。有没有办法将二者合二为一，完美笔记体验的方法呢？</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>受王树义老师和江sir视频的引路，发现了roam/css大法。原来roam是支持代码嵌入的，也就是JS和CSS这种代码块，是可以直接在笔记系统中生效的。那我们就可以用CSS代码开发自己的笔记UI系统了。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><span>具体方法</span></span>","level":3},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"ordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>在roam里添加roam/css</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"方法一：可以直接写CSS片段，将其转换成CSS，就可以直接生效","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span><span>方法二：或者可以将CSS片段、变量保存在github上，并用@import语法拉入本地的CSS代码片段。这种比较推荐，因为有很多大神已经做好设计了，我们直接将它们拿回来用就好了，不必自己全盘造轮子（主要是懒）</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>对于白嫖本地端的白嫖党来说，第二种方式很重要。因为网上大神的方案一般是适配web端的，拉到本地端用有些主题效果就变样了，需要自己调整适配一下。这样就可以将方法一、二结合起来，先用github的远程CSS片段，自己再对其中的变量进行修改，就能得到自己需要的效果了。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>比如，我很喜欢的Bear主题，可以使用以下片段拉入本地端渲染主题：</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span><code>@import url('https://rcvd.github.io/roam-css-system/themes/bear.css');</code></span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>这个主题非常漂亮，美中不足的是，一些字体在本地端显示得太小了，阅读起来很吃力。我们在原主题的基础上，抓取部分片段、变量，对其进行本地端的优化适配。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>可以使用开发者工具（ctrl+shift+i）来进行定位，找到影响UI效果的变量。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>在<code></code>:root {}<code></code>内进行添加修改</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>全局字体和字体大小的调整</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>页面标题</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>基础文本</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>二级、三级标题</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>我最终的roam/css代码:</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<br>"},"common":{}}],"typeset":"typeset-1687836132043","layout":"web","basic":{"title":"","cover":"","summary":""}}